        "text": "I’m not aware of any FoC style meetups here, but there are a couple hackerspaces at least? Noise bridge is one that my friends go to.\n\nI’d definitely recommend hanging out at Golden Gate Park and ocean beach. Fort Funston beach is breathtaking too :)\n\nI’ll be outta town until the ~28th, otherwise I’d offer to grab coffee and show you some research microscopes!",
